<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="C" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Covering" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Covering,</orth> subst. == cover: <cit><quote>bring some c. for this naked soul,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 4.1.46" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 1, 46</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>without c., save yon field of stars,</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 1.1.37" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. I, 1, 37</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>under the c. of a careful night,</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 1.2.81" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 2, 81</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>